description:
&lt;h1&gt;PA to Essex Health &amp; Justice Service Manager &amp; Administrator to TeamBand 4 - £21,892 - £24,157 per annumBased - C &amp; E Centre&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking to recruit a highly motivated and enthusiastic individual to join our team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will be responsible for liaising with professionals from various disciplines such as prison, police, courts, probation, GP’s as well as relatives, careers and service users.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;They will be the main focal point of contact for other staff and agencies referring to the service and ensuring the referrals are processed in a timely manner.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;They will be expected to transcribe reports in an efficient and timely manner for the psychiatrists that are working in court on the same day. Also to be involved in developing information systems when required.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder should have excellent computer skills and be able to prioritise their workload to meet demanding deadlines. The post holder should be capable of using their own initiative within a busy office.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will be the focal point for people contacting the service and should have excellent customer service skills and be able to communicate at all levels.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will be undertake PA duties for the Service Manager&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;EPUT are looking for motivated staff who shares our Trust values of Open, Compassionate and Empowering. In return, EPUT can offer you a range of benefits and development including;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Season Ticket Loans&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;NHS discounts for staff&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent Training facilities and opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Buying and Selling annual leave scheme&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The opportunity to work bank shifts and expand knowledge and experience in other areas&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Salary Sacrifice schemes including lease cars and Cycle to Work&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name Janet Childs&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job title Interim Service Manager&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address janet.childs@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
